Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph <archive-uri> create

Purpose:
  Create an LLM Wiki archive from source material at source stage.

Usage:
  wikigraph <archive-uri> create [source] [--input-format <format>] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>]

Contract:
  - Mutates: yes, writes the archive path.
  - LLM: no; create stops at source stage.
  - stdin: supported with --input-format markdown or txt.
  - JSON: no.

Examples:
  wikigraph wkg://book.sdpub create ./book.md --input-format markdown
  wikigraph wkg://empty.sdpub create
  cat article.md | wikigraph wkg://article.sdpub create --input-format markdown
